('deposit_payment_reminder_email_body', '<p>Dear [FIRST_NAME] [LAST_NAME]</p>\r\n<p>Please access to  <strong>[DEPOSIT_PAYMENT_LINK] </strong>to complete pay for your registration <strong>#[REGISTRATION_ID] </strong>of event [EVENT_TITLE]. The amount you have to pay is <strong>[AMOUNT]</strong></p>\r\n<p>Regards,</p>\r\n<p>Website administrator team</p>');